{
  "texts": [
    "The critical detail to remember is that the type of data generated depends highly on the precision of the prompt sent to the industrial chatbot.",
    "It should be modeled as per the application requirement after several tests.",
    "In our experiments, we obtained two types of data generation per industrial chatbot version.",
    "The online version outcome looks closer to the loaded data sample than the offline model.",
    "Here is the prompt with which we test our chatbots for the synthetic data generation feature:-Generate five new observations in a table with different faults detected.Figures 13 and 14 are the synthetic data generation prompt results in the online and offline bot versions."
  ]
}